VS-LIVE-3 — Click LinkedIn → reaches LinkedIn share flow
---------------------------------------------------------
Action: Playwright click on a[data-share-target="linkedin"]
New tab URL:
  https://www.linkedin.com/uas/login?session_redirect=
    https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2FshareArticle%2F%3Furl%3D
      https%253A%252F%252Femail-centered-wondering-classics.trycloudflare.com
        %252Farchive%252Fe426a851-8af7-4a78-8ca3-f2c6a881e684

Notes:
- LinkedIn detected unauthenticated session and redirected to /uas/login.
- session_redirect carries the original /shareArticle/?url=<our-archive>
  URL with proper double-encoding (the URL-inside-an-URL).
- After login, LinkedIn brings the user to the composer prefilled with
  our archive URL. Preview headline/description are scraped server-side
  from the URL's og: tags (see Known Limitation below).
RESULT: PASS

